<blockquote>
<p>[!TIP]
<strong>How to succeed in this week</strong>:
This week is the bridge from on-premise to cloud thinking. The shift from "servers" to "services" is fundamental. Pay attention to the business drivers for cloud adoption—technical skills alone aren't enough.</p>
